channel.title: Unused Half life enemy?
channel.description:
Unused Half life enemy?
A few days ago I was just being bored on my pc while browsing hl1 audio files. when suddenly I found a map witch said: x. I clicked on it and I couldnt recognise the sounds. An unused beta/alpha enemy maybe? Im really curious. maybe you guys know what it is. (the location is: steam>steamapps>common>half life>valve>sound>x)
